{"id":7164,"content":"<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><BR><FONT size=3 face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;<SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</SPAN>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</FONT></SPAN><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">《炎黄春秋》</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">2009</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">9</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月号上发表周有光老先生的《纪念端午节的意义》一文，言简意赅、振聋发聩。作者提出端午节应</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">发展成为尊重知识的节日，解放知识分子的节日</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">怀念古代为的是教育今日</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">……</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">阅读古书而不知</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">‘</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">以古鉴今</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">’</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，读书何用？纪念端午节，自然地从屈原的受难联想到秦始皇的焚书坑儒，历代的文字狱，以及晚近的反右运动</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">言论可以控制，记忆无法禁止</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">。</SPAN></FONT><SPAN lang=EN-US><BR><FONT size=3 face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp; <SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;</SPAN>&nbsp;&nbsp;</FONT></SPAN><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">作者写道：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">屈原被否定，放逐异乡，心力交悴，投水自尽，这跟反右运动中知识分子被否定，下放劳动改造，折磨而死或失望自尽，历史轮回，何其鲜活！田汉的自沉、老舍的自沉，储安平的失踪，一代知识精英被摧残</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">。这里的</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">田汉的自沉</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">不确。</SPAN></FONT><SPAN lang=EN-US><BR><FONT size=3 face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;<SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </SPAN>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</FONT></SPAN><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">著名剧作家、诗人田汉，于</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">文革</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">期间的</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1966</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">12</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">4</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">日被捕。罪名有：人家</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">大写十三年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，而他大写历史剧；人家突出工农兵，他却突出</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">名古洋</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">；他的《谢瑶环》等剧是大毒草</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">……</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">在家中抓走时他安慰老母亲说：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">妈妈，您多保重。您放心吧，事情总会弄清楚的。我会再回来的。</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">在狱中，各种折磨使他原就患有的糖尿病、肾病和心脏病日渐一日地加重，后来被改叫李五住进北京</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">301</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">医院。</SPAN></FONT><SPAN lang=EN-US><BR><FONT size=3 face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </SPAN>&nbsp;&nbsp;1968</FONT></SPAN><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">12</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">9</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">日，处于弥留状态，他提出要求：</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">我家里还有一个老妈妈，做梦都想见到她，你们让我在死以前回去看她一眼吧！</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">可怜的要求被断然拒绝。这位</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">新中国的莎士比亚</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">、</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">当代的关汉卿</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">带着对</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">96</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">岁老母深挚的眷念，于</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">1968</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">12</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">10</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">日凌晨</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">3</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">点凄凉地见莎士比亚和关汉卿去了，时年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">70</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">岁。</SPAN></FONT><SPAN lang=EN-US><BR><FONT size=3 face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </SPAN>&nbsp;&nbsp;1979</FONT></SPAN><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">年</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">4</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">月得到平反昭雪。</SPAN></FONT><SPAN lang=EN-US><BR><FONT size=3 face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp; <SPAN style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;</SPAN>&nbsp;&nbsp;“</FONT></SPAN><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">文革</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">中田汉是受迫害致死，并非</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">自沉</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，这是一。二、文章都已经点到</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">提倡</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">‘</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">知识无用论</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">’</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">、</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">‘</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">知识越多越反动</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">’</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">的</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">文革</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">要害，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">文革</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">对当代知识分子的迫害比起</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">反右运动</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">有过之而无不及，在联想到</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">晚近的反右运动</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">后若加上</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">和文化大革命</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">几个字，岂不更好？三、文中</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">心力交悴</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">的</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">悴</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，现代汉语词典的解释即</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">憔悴</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">，形容人瘦弱，面色不好看，那是外在的；而</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">瘁</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”——</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">过度劳累，</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">心力交悴</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">不如用</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">“</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">心力交瘁</SPAN><SPAN lang=EN-US><FONT face=\"Times New Roman\">”</FONT></SPAN><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-hansi-font-family: Times New Roman\">准确。后两点像似编辑审稿的一时疏忽。</SPAN></FONT><SPAN lang=EN-US><BR><BR></SPAN><FONT size=3><SPAN style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana\">（该文所表述的内容为作者本人观点，与《炎黄春秋》杂志及炎黄春秋网的观点和立场无关。）</SPAN><SPAN style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\" lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></FONT></P>\r\n<P style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=MsoNormal><SPAN lang=EN-US><o:p><FONT size=3 face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>","title":"田汉非“自沉”","time":1270147401000}